reviews.comment: Drupal isn't for amateurs. Merely installing it can be grueling, so be sure you hire someone who actually understands it.
Riaz was very knowledgable about Drupal. I recommend him highly to any one need updates, changes, and maintentance on their Drupal website.
Riaz did a good job as always. I especially appreciate how easy he is to reach whenever I have questions.

Riaz did an amazing job! He helped me with the environment of the website, created the homepage in Drupal, and even conducted a training session so I could manage everything on my own. Communication with him was great – he always responded quickly, explained everything clearly, and was super patient. It’s clear he knows his stuff and really understands what the client needs. I’m really happy with the results and will definitely reach out to him again in the future! :)
Very quick response...didnt took long to fix.
